                    <video
                        class="w-1/2 lg:w-full mx-auto lg:mx-0"
                        src="https://video.wixstatic.com/video/68b7af_a0efad12ce3240b3a680a2bb3bec5f72/1080p/mp4/file.mp4"
                        autoplay
                        muted
                        loop></video>
                    <h3
                        class="lg:hidden -mt-2 text-xl lg:text-2xl 2xl:text-3xl font-bold text-trangerine text-center lg:text-left"
                    >
                        ¡Ahora sin costo fijo!
                    </h3>
                    <div class="text-center lg:text-left mt-8 lg:hidden">
                        <a
                            href="/"
                            target="_blank"
                            class="inline-block bg-blue-munsell text-white py-2 px-8 rounded font-bold hover:bg-trangerine duration-300"
